data.description: ASSUMABLE 5% RATE! SAVE $ & GET LAST YEARS RATE TODAY! Recently Renovated this 2 Bed, 2 Bath home is Move in Ready. Highlights include Newer Flooring > Kitchen Cabinets > Quartz Counters > Custom Backsplash > Roof > Upgraded Bathrooms with Custom Tiled Surrounds > Stone Counter Vanities & more! All located on a Huge lot with an oversized 720 SqFt detached garage for those bigger toys or additional storage needs. Large covered deck in rear, Property completely Fenced, Private Well and No HOA. Don't miss out and contact the listing agent for details on assuming the rate and to schedule your showing today!
